=item B<_story_printable>

 _story_printable topic story_id

Shows a complete story, in 'printer-friendly' format.
=cut

<div class = 'story_printable'>

	{-story_body|$0|$1}

	<p>
	<div class = 'tags'>Etiquetas: {-foreach|{-story_tags|$0|$1}|\{-_search_tag\|\$0\|$1\}|, }</div>
	</p>

	<hr>

	<div class = 'self_links'>
		Enlace permanente a esta p&aacute;gina:
		<a href='{-aurl|STORY|topic|$0|id|$1}'>{-aurl|STORY|topic|$0|id|$1}</a>
	</div>

</div>
